When set_property_chain fails to find the property chain on the immediate
object, fall back to traversing all descendants. This handles glTF-loaded
meshes where the scene root (`<object>`) is a THREE.Group and the actual
Mesh nodes with materials reside in the child hierarchy (e.g.,
`<object>/Scene/Cube`).

